data.name: GPMsDB-tk
data.description: Genomically predicted protein mass database (GPMsDB) toolkits for assigning taxonomic identification of bacterial and archaeal cells with user-provided MALDI-TOF mass spectrometry profiles

evidence: "GPMsDB-tk/GPMsDB-dbtk are software toolkits for assigning taxonomic identification to user-provided MALDI-TOF mass spectrometry profiles" (end-user analysis toolkit).
Install instructions use git clone and setup.py from the repository: "git clone https://github.com/ysekig/GPMsDB-tk" and "python setup.py install" (source-based distribution).

Copyright and contact indicate a single primary author: "Copyright (C) 2023 Yuji Sekiguchi, National Institute of Advanced Industrial Science and Technology (AIST)" and "contact Yuji Sekiguchi (y.sekiguchi@aist.go.jp)".
